description:
An Upper Floor Feature Presentation
When the New Maid, played by delicious newcomer Kasey Warner, stumbles upon Roman Nomar's personal Sex Toy, latex clad barbie Christie Stevens, the flirtatious newbie cannot resist playing with the goods. But when Master Nomar catches the Maid with her mouth in Christie's cookies, he makes them both pay the price for breaking the House Rules.
title: The Sex Toy and the New Maid
